snippet.title: Action Quake 2 (Original Xbox) - Online Multiplayer 2021
snippet.description:
Played via TCP/IP on https://www.gametracker.com/server_info/gaming.widowmakers.com:10024/ using Quake 2x (2002) homebrew port by Repi with AQ2 mod install.

0:00 - Cloud (various rounds)
2:13 - de_dust (various rounds)
9:27 - Wfall
15:45 - Cliff2
21:34 - Airport
29:06 - air747

Recorded by Demon27248
___________________________________________________

Join our community here!
https://discord.gg/D9DJUhJ and also check out http://sixthgengaming.com

Playing Original Xbox games online is still possible as of 2021.

XLink Kai is a program that runs on your PC which allows you to play system link enabled games for Original Xbox, Xbox 360, PS2, PS3, PSP and Gamecube online against other players. You can download the program from https://teamxlink.co.uk

#OriginalXbox #XLinkKai #ActionQuake2
